    <header>
        <h1><span class="title" itemprop="name" data-bind="text:title">Oberhausen On Tour</span></h1>
    </header>

    <img class="picture pull-right img-responsive" itemprop="image" data-fieldname="picture" src="/media/cache/c1/6e/c16edb5274ed838ab0ad7afd328d9288.jpg" width="400" height="200" data-src="/static/img/events/267595323_640.jpg" data-width="640" data-height="320" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#img-picture-1360" alt="" data-bind="attr: { src: pictureData().displaySrc, width: pictureData().displayWidth, height: pictureData().displayHeight, 'data-src': pictureData().src, 'data-width': pictureData().width, 'data-height': pictureData().height }" /><div class="modal " id="img-picture-1360">    <div class="modal-dialog">        <div class="modal-content">            <div class="modal-header">                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">                    &times;                </button>            </div>            <div class="modal-body">                <img src="/static/img/events/267595323_640.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="" data-bind="attr: {src: pictureData().displaySrc}">            </div>        </div>    </div></div>

    <h3><time class="startDate" datetime="2013-04-03" data-bind="attr:{datetime:startDateTime()},text:displayStart()">Wednesday 3 April</time> to <time class="endDate" datetime="2013-05-17" data-bind="attr:{datetime:endDateTime()},text:displayEnd()">Friday 17 May 2013</time></h3>

    <meta itemprop="image" content="/media/cache/c1/6e/c16edb5274ed838ab0ad7afd328d9288.jpg">

    <div class="bodysection">
        <div class="body" itemprop="about" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body"><p><span>The Oberhausen Film Festival, founded in 1954, is one of the oldest
short film festivals in the world and one of the major international platforms
for the short form.</span></p><p><span>We’re very
pleased to be hosting 6 screenings of some of their best films from 2012, from
incredible music videos to political films, and going through artist film and
video work.</span></p>
</div>
    </div>

    </div>

    <header class="row">
        <h3></h3>
    </header>

    <div class="smallsublist">
        <header>
            <h3>Films in the Oberhausen On Tour:</h3>
        </header>
        
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxb mo0413"
                     data-href="/on/film/1184">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/5b/41/5b41141b06d9989635dcaffb2cb831bd.jpg"/>
                        
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive visible-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/6b/13/6b132dc53af975d564cddff9895df89e.jpg"/>
                        
                    
                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">03</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1184">Oberhausen On Tour: Children Programme</a></h1>

                <h2>3 Apr 2013, 4 p.m.</h2>

                <p>This afternoon we’ll have a special screening for the wee-ones, with fabulous live action and animation short films from Taiwan, continental Europe and the UK.</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1184">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxa mo0413"
                     data-href="/on/film/1147">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/0d/a6/0da6d0dc2a4e9b4b423c6701400ab416.jpg"/>
                        
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive visible-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/0e/ea/0eea08a0607db6e49bdd9051bcad17e7.jpg"/>
                        
                    
                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">03</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1147">Oberhausen On Tour: Music Videos Programme + German Music Dj In The Bar!</a></h1>

                <h2>3 Apr 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>A very special night showcasing some of the best German music videos
from the Oberhausen Film Festival 2012! Not exactly the typical MTV-videos –
expect interesting animation and lots of creativity for great undiscovered independent
bands.</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1147">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxb mo0413"
                     data-href="/on/film/1148">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/44/a9/44a9d8291b5afdf42e40c2849e2662ae.jpg"/>
                        
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive visible-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/90/ea/90ea276409a8443736aa097209bbe62a.jpg"/>
                        
                    
                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">10</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1148">Oberhausen On Tour: Resistance Programme</a></h1>

                <h2>10 Apr 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>This film programme includes some of the most important political works shown in the Oberhausen Film Festival (one the oldest short film festivals in the world) and have won awards there. In these films, dating from 1961 to 2010, filmmakers intervene, take a stand and protest on behalf of human rights, freedom and life. </p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1148">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxa mo0413"
                     data-href="/on/film/1149">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/eb/0f/eb0f26fd1cdf60fe4df93b9fbe7a7cde.jpg"/>
                        
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive visible-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/b5/2d/b52d6af06c0a180d588e9965cc000ec8.jpg"/>
                        
                    
                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">17</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1149">Oberhausen On Tour: International Competition</a></h1>

                <h2>17 Apr 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>That night will feature some of the best international short films from
the Oberhausen Film Festival – which are probably some of the best in the
world! A very special hour-long programme.</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1149">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxb mo0513"
                     data-href="/on/film/1150">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/d8/2c/d82c046a73608a5be0a42cd4d28690b8.jpg"/>
                        
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive visible-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/3f/48/3f48fe342df67a98e3de390f0b9a2f53.jpg"/>
                        
                    
                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">01</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1150">Oberhausen On Tour: German Competition + Gdr Revisited</a></h1>

                <h2>1 May 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>This screening will feature 2 programmes of short films: one programme with
some of the best German short films in competition at the Oberhausen Film
Festival 2012, and one programme of shorts that take look at the role that artists,
sportsmen and intellectuals played in what was the German Democratic Republic (East
Germany).</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1150">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
            <section class="row dmod clickable boxa mo0513"
                     data-href="/on/film/1151">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    
                        
                            <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" alt="" src="/media/cache/af/89/af89c9f286f46421fa5b54333107340c.jpg"/>
                        
                        
